    dc:creator "Ho, - Z." ;
    dc:date "2019" ;
    dc:title "The Luciolinae of S. E. Asia and the Australopacific region: a revisionary checklist (Coleoptera: Lampyridae) including description of three new genera and 13 new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3508102>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3508123>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3508127> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3508102>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1−8. Key to genera characters 1. 1, 2 Australoluciola anthracina type male (MNHN); 3, 4 Aus. japenensis paratype male; 5, 6 Atyphella scabra male; 7, 8 Aty. leucura type male (MNHN). 1, 2, 5, 6 aedeagus ventral (1, 5), and dorsal (2, 6) (lateral lobes are arrowed). 3, 4, 7, 8 aedeagal sheath dorsal (3, 7), and ventral (4, 8). Oblique arrows in anterior section indicate point where tergite arms join the lateral margins of the sheath sternite; vertical arrow pointing to foot of page in 3 indicates anterior margin of sheath tergite; vertical and horizontal lines in 4 indicate length (vertical) and width (horizontal) of sheath sternite; lower paired arrows in 8 indicate emarginated margin of sheath sternite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3508102/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3508123>
    dc:description "FIGURES 57–63. Key to genera characters 9. 57, 58 Atyphella aphrogeneia; 59 Lloydiella majuscula; 60, 61 Ll. japenensis; 62, 63 Convexa wolfi. 57, 58 aedeagal sheath dorsal (57) and ventral (arrows indicates emargination of right side of sheath sternite); 59 dorsal and ventral, and 63 dorsal habitus; 60–62 aedeagus, 60 slightly right lateral; 61, 62 ventral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3508123/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3508127>
    dc:description "FIGURES 64–69. Key to genera characters 10. 64 Aquilonia costata; 65, 66 Aq. similismessoria comb. nov.; 67 Magnalata limbata; 68 Atyphella flammans; 69 Aty. aphrogeneia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3508127/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

